name: TototroSupermanChopperCinderella
description: An omnipotent figure known as CINMANTORO arose in the world of cryptocurrencies. The creature came to challenge the stereotypes of the crypto world with it's enigmatic and amorphous look, which could change at will. CINMAN'S goal was to cure the scourge of poverty that afflicted the crypto environment and bestow vast wealth upon those who put their faith in the power of $TSLA.
